{
  "stem": "13623.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And suddenly, we hear the locomotive starting, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and we're moving.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We don't know where we're moving, but the train started to move.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We're on the-- we were on the train for a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We looked through the-- the crevice of the-- of the railroad-- of the cattle car.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we see a town called Kaschau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We are in Hungary at this point.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The train stops.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We're surrounded with guards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Nobody gets off the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But those labor battalions that I was mentioning before-- when they took the guys of military age and they gave them yellow arm bands-- they let them bring us water.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "As they let them bring us water, they opened the car to give us the water.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Some of these guys recognizes a sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Some of these guys recognizes a sweetheart, a mother, a father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But there's nothing they cannot-- there's nothing that they can do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They gave us water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They had to walk away from us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The train was continuing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As the train goes for another several days, the stench is terrible.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There was no-- was no-- no wheres to go to a bathroom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the-- the adults sort of do everything they can to wait until dark sets in, because they-- there was no-- no wheres to-- no sanitary facilities.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was-- it was-- the stench was getting worse from day to day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After several days, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] somebody looked through, again, those crevices.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they see we're passing a railroad station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the name is Krakow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We-- it didn't mean anything to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was a little boy.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
